data.description: Great opportunity to own a 4-bedroom house with spectacular views of the Rogue Valley! Situated on over half an acre overlooking the Rogue Valley, this tastefully updated home enjoys great outdoor spaces and an efficient 4 bed/2 bath floor plan. As you approach the home, the paved driveway leads to the landscaped front yard overlooking a lower terrace with garden area and potential for more parking. Inside you'll find an updated living room w/ fireplace, dining, and bright galley kitchen. Accessed from living room, the large 4th bedroom provides ample private space and storage. Down the hallway, there's 3 spacious bedrooms with good natural light and a full bathroom. The backyard, accessed from a large sliding door, features open space perfect for finishing as a beautiful patio, with a majority of the property continuing further behind the home. This unique home with incredible views provides a great opportunity! OWNER WILL CARRY!
